         <abstract id="aspace_1c92e447994dd47a30a9f6f69406f6b8">An artificial collection of postcards, totaling approximately 6,000 items, transferred from the Schneelock-Bacon family, Gilman family, Beecher-Scoville family, and Pforzheimer papers, and miscellaneous additions.</abstract>
    
