      <odd id="aspace_df99a71452ebd732c89626f9572f7661">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>No further transfers of postcards from collections will be made. Additions to this collection may consist of postcards accessioned individually or en masse, which do not warrant collection status.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_7da2768622bf0964c165dfa7c5c1f7ea">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>
         <p>May only be used under the supervison of a reference archivist.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
