      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_c9f424645afb2151d0ab8635e9521ca7">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Historical Postcard Collection. Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_db8d6ee018621fe5d20083bebe0c58ab">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>An artificial collection of postcards, totaling approximately 6,000 items, transferred from the Schneelock-Bacon family, Gilman family, Beecher-Scoville family, and Pforzheimer papers, and miscellaneous additions.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_2b8efcde254d9e2c57ad9431f511d8f3">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged by family name, individual, or subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
